 <tr id="token-current-user--field-country--metatag--og--audio--secure-url" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-country--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Audio secure URL</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-country:metatag:og:audio:secure_url]</a></td><td>The secure URL to an audio file that complements this object. All "http://" URLs will automatically be converted to "https://".</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-country--metatag--og--audio--type" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-country--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Audio type</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-country:metatag:og:audio:type]</a></td><td>The MIME type of the audio file. Examples include "application/mp3" for an MP3 file.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-country--metatag--author" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-country--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Author URL</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-country:metatag:author]</a></td><td>Used by some search engines to confirm authorship of the content on a page. Should be either the full URL for the author's Google+ profile page or a local page with information about the author.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-country--metatag--book--isbn" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-country--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Book's ISBN</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-country:metatag:book:isbn]</a></td><td>The book's <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number">International Standard Book Number</a>, which may be in one of several formats.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-country--metatag--book--author" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-country--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Book's author</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-country:metatag:book:author]</a></td><td>Links to the book's author's Facebook profile, should be either URLs to the author's profile page or their Facebook profile IDs.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-country--metatag--book--release-date" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-country--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Book release date</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-country:metatag:book:release_date]</a></td><td>The date this content will expire, with an optional time value. Needs to be in <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_8601">ISO 8601</a> format.</td> </tr>

 <tr id="token-current-user--field-country--metatag--og--updated-time" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-country--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Content modification date &amp; time</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-country:metatag:og:updated_time]</a></td><td>The date this content was last modified, with an optional time value. Needs to be in <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_8601">ISO 8601</a> format. Can be the same as the 'Article modification date' tag.</td> </tr>

The default ignores this value, the 'Automatic' value should be sufficient if this is actually needed.</td> </tr>

 <tr id="token-current-user--field-country--metatag--news-keywords" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-country--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Google News Keywords</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-country:metatag:news_keywords]</a></td><td>A comma-separated list of keywords about the page.  <tr id="token-current-user--field-country--metatag--standout" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-country--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Google Standout</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-country:metatag:standout]</a></td><td>Highlight standout journalism on the web, especially for breaking news; used as an indicator in <a href="https://support.google.com/news/publisher/answer/191283?hl=en&amp;ref_topic=2484650">Google News</a>. Warning: Don't abuse it, to be used a maximum of 7 times per calendar week!</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-country--metatag--icbm" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-country--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>ICBM</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-country:metatag:icbm]</a></td><td>Geo-spatial information in "latitude, longitude" format, e.g. "50.167958, -97.133185"; <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ICBM">see Wikipedia for details</a>.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-country--metatag--og--image" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-country--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Image</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-country:metatag:og:image]</a></td><td>The URL of an image which should represent the content. For best results use an image that is at least 1200 x 630 pixels in size, but at least 600 x 316 pixels is a recommended minimum. Supports PNG, JPEG and GIF formats. Should not be used if og:image:url is used.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-country--metatag--image-src" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-country--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Image</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-country:metatag:image_src]</a></td><td>An image associated with this page, for use as a thumbnail in social networks and other services.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-country--metatag--og--image--url" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-country--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Image URL</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-country:metatag:og:image:url]</a></td><td>A alternative version of og:image and has exactly the same requirements; only one needs to be used.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-country--metatag--og--image--height" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-country--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Image height</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-country:metatag:og:image:height]</a></td><td>The height of the above image(s). Note: if both the unsecured and secured images are provided, they should both be the same size.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-country--metatag--og--image--type" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-country--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Image type</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-country:metatag:og:image:type]</a></td><td>The type of image referenced above. Should be either "image/gif" for a GIF image, "image/jpeg" for a JPG/JPEG image, or "image/png" for a PNG image. Note: there should be one value for each image, and having more than there are images may cause problems.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-country--metatag--og--image--width" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-country--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Image width</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-country:metatag:og:image:width]</a></td><td>The width of the above image(s). If the full URL is not known it is acceptable to use a partial URL or just the domain name.</td> </tr>

 <tr id="token-current-user--field-country--metatag--referrer" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-country--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Referrer policy</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-country:metatag:referrer]</a></td><td>Indicate to search engines and other page scrapers whether or not links should be followed.  <tr id="token-current-user--field-country--metatag--refresh" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-country--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Refresh</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-country:metatag:refresh]</a></td><td>The number of seconds to wait before refreshing the page. May also force redirect to another page using the format "5; url=http://example.com/", which would be triggered after five seconds.</td> </tr>

 <tr id="token-current-user--field-country-of-interest--metatag--rating" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-country-of-interest--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Content rating</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-country-of-interest:metatag:rating]</a></td><td>Used to indicate the intended audience for the content.</td> </tr>

 <tr id="token-current-user--field-country-of-interest--metatag--og--determiner" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-country-of-interest--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Content title determiner</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-country-of-interest:metatag:og:determiner]</a></td><td>The word that appears before the content's title in a sentence. The default ignores this value, the 'Automatic' value should be sufficient if this is actually needed.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-country-of-interest--metatag--og--type" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-country-of-interest--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Content type</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-country-of-interest:metatag:og:type]</a></td><td>The type of the content, e.g., <em>movie</em>.</td> </tr>

The description meta tag may be used by search engines to display a snippet about the page in search results.</td> </tr>

 <tr id="token-current-user--field-country-of-interest--metatag--news-keywords" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-country-of-interest--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Google News Keywords</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-country-of-interest:metatag:news_keywords]</a></td><td>A comma-separated list of keywords about the page.  <tr id="token-current-user--field-country-of-interest--metatag--standout" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-country-of-interest--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Google Standout</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-country-of-interest:metatag:standout]</a></td><td>Highlight standout journalism on the web, especially for breaking news; used as an indicator in <a href="https://support.google.com/news/publisher/answer/191283?hl=en&amp;ref_topic=2484650">Google News</a>. Warning: Don't abuse it, to be used a maximum of 7 times per calendar week!</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-country-of-interest--metatag--icbm" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-country-of-interest--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>ICBM</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-country-of-interest:metatag:icbm]</a></td><td>Geo-spatial information in "latitude, longitude" format, e.g. "50.167958, -97.133185"; <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ICBM">see Wikipedia for details</a>.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-country-of-interest--metatag--og--image" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-country-of-interest--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Image</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-country-of-interest:metatag:og:image]</a></td><td>The URL of an image which should represent the content. For best results use an image that is at least 1200 x 630 pixels in size, but at least 600 x 316 pixels is a recommended minimum. Supports PNG, JPEG and GIF formats. Should not be used if og:image:url is used.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-country-of-interest--metatag--image-src" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-country-of-interest--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Image</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-country-of-interest:metatag:image_src]</a></td><td>An image associated with this page, for use as a thumbnail in social networks and other services.</td> </tr>

 <tr id="token-current-user--field-country-of-interest--metatag--og--image--height" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-country-of-interest--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Image height</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-country-of-interest:metatag:og:image:height]</a></td><td>The height of the above image(s). Note: if both the unsecured and secured images are provided, they should both be the same size.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-country-of-interest--metatag--og--image--type" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-country-of-interest--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Image type</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-country-of-interest:metatag:og:image:type]</a></td><td>The type of image referenced above. Should be either "image/gif" for a GIF image, "image/jpeg" for a JPG/JPEG image, or "image/png" for a PNG image. Note: there should be one value for each image, and having more than there are images may cause problems.</td> </tr>

May also force redirect to another page using the format "5; url=http://example.com/", which would be triggered after five seconds.</td> </tr>

 <tr id="token-current-user--field-country-of-interest--metatag--rights" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-country-of-interest--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Rights</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-country-of-interest:metatag:rights]</a></td><td>Details about intellectual property, such as copyright or trademarks; does not automatically protect the site's content or intellectual property.</td> </tr>

 <tr id="token-current-user--field-country-of-interest--metatag--og--image--secure-url" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-country-of-interest--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Secure image URL</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-country-of-interest:metatag:og:image:secure_url]</a></td><td>The secure URL (HTTPS) of an image which should represent the content. The default ignores this value, the 'Automatic' value should be sufficient if this is actually needed.</td> </tr>

Warning: Don't abuse it, to be used a maximum of 7 times per calendar week!</td> </tr>

For best results use an image that is at least 1200 x 630 pixels in size, but at least 600 x 316 pixels is a recommended minimum. Supports PNG, JPEG and GIF formats. Should not be used if og:image:url is used.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--feed-node--metatag--image-src" class="child-of-token-current-user--feed-node--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Image</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:feed-node:metatag:image_src]</a></td><td>An image associated with this page, for use as a thumbnail in social networks and other services.</td> </tr>

 <tr id="token-current-user--feed-node--metatag--og--image--height" class="child-of-token-current-user--feed-node--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Image height</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:feed-node:metatag:og:image:height]</a></td><td>The height of the above image(s).  <tr id="token-current-user--feed-node--metatag--og--image--type" class="child-of-token-current-user--feed-node--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Image type</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:feed-node:metatag:og:image:type]</a></td><td>The type of image referenced above. Should be either "image/gif" for a GIF image, "image/jpeg" for a JPG/JPEG image, or "image/png" for a PNG image. Note: there should be one value for each image, and having more than there are images may cause problems.</td> </tr>

 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--article--section" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Article section</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:article:section]</a></td><td>The primary section of this website the content belongs to.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--article--tag" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Article tag(s)</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:article:tag]</a></td><td>Appropriate keywords for this content.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--og--audio" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Audio URL</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:og:audio]</a></td><td>The URL to an audio file that complements this object.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--og--audio--secure-url" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Audio secure URL</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:og:audio:secure_url]</a></td><td>The secure URL to an audio file that complements this object. All "http://" URLs will automatically be converted to "https://".</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--og--audio--type" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Audio type</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:og:audio:type]</a></td><td>The MIME type of the audio file. Examples include "application/mp3" for an MP3 file.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--author" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Author URL</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:author]</a></td><td>Used by some search engines to confirm authorship of the content on a page. Should be either the full URL for the author's Google+ profile page or a local page with information about the author.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--book--isbn" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Book's ISBN</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:book:isbn]</a></td><td>The book's <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number">International Standard Book Number</a>, which may be in one of several formats.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--book--author" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Book's author</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:book:author]</a></td><td>Links to the book's author's Facebook profile, should be either URLs to the author's profile page or their Facebook profile IDs.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--book--release-date" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Book release date</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:book:release_date]</a></td><td>The date this content will expire, with an optional time value. Needs to be in <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_8601">ISO 8601</a> format.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--book--tag" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Book tags</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:book:tag]</a></td><td>Appropriate keywords for this book.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--canonical" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Canonical URL</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:canonical]</a></td><td>Preferred page location or URL to help eliminate duplicate content for search engines.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--og--description" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Content description</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:og:description]</a></td><td>A one to two sentence description of the content.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--content-language" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Content language</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:content-language]</a></td><td>A deprecated meta tag for defining this page's two-letter language code(s).</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--og--updated-time" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Content modification date &amp; time</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:og:updated_time]</a></td><td>The date this content was last modified, with an optional time value. Needs to be in <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_8601">ISO 8601</a> format. Can be the same as the 'Article modification date' tag.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--rating" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Content rating</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:rating]</a></td><td>Used to indicate the intended audience for the content.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--og--title" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Content title</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:og:title]</a></td><td>The title of the content, e.g., <em>The Rock</em>.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--og--determiner" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Content title determiner</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:og:determiner]</a></td><td>The word that appears before the content's title in a sentence. The default ignores this value, the 'Automatic' value should be sufficient if this is actually needed.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--og--type" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Content type</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:og:type]</a></td><td>The type of the content, e.g., <em>movie</em>.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--og--country-name" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Country name</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:og:country_name]</a></td><td></td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--description" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Description</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:description]</a></td><td>A brief and concise summary of the page's content, preferably 150 characters or less. The description meta tag may be used by search engines to display a snippet about the page in search results.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--video--director" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Director(s)</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:video:director]</a></td><td>Links to the Facebook profiles for director(s) that worked on the video.</td> </tr>

 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--profile--first-name" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>First name</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:profile:first_name]</a></td><td>The first name of the person who's Profile page this is.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--profile--gender" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Gender</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:profile:gender]</a></td><td>Any of Facebook's gender values should be allowed, the initial two being 'male' and 'female'.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--generator" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Generator</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:generator]</a></td><td>Describes the name and version number of the software or publishing tool used to create the page.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--geo.placename" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Geo place name</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:geo.placename]</a></td><td>A location's formal name.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--geo.position" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Geo position</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:geo.position]</a></td><td>Geo-spatial information in "latitude;longitude" format, e.g. "50.167958;-97.133185"; <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Geotagging#HTML_pages">see Wikipedia for details</a>.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--geo.region" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Geo region</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:geo.region]</a></td><td>A location's two-letter international country code, with an optional two-letter region, e.g. "US-NH" for New Hampshire in the USA.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--news-keywords" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Google News Keywords</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:news_keywords]</a></td><td>A comma-separated list of keywords about the page. This meta tag is used as an indicator in <a href="http://support.google.com/news/publisher/bin/answer.py?hl=en&amp;answer=68297">Google News</a>.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--standout" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Google Standout</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:standout]</a></td><td>Highlight standout journalism on the web, especially for breaking news; used as an indicator in <a href="https://support.google.com/news/publisher/answer/191283?hl=en&amp;ref_topic=2484650">Google News</a>. Warning: Don't abuse it, to be used a maximum of 7 times per calendar week!</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--icbm" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>ICBM</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:icbm]</a></td><td>Geo-spatial information in "latitude, longitude" format, e.g. "50.167958, -97.133185"; <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ICBM">see Wikipedia for details</a>.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--og--image" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Image</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:og:image]</a></td><td>The URL of an image which should represent the content. For best results use an image that is at least 1200 x 630 pixels in size, but at least 600 x 316 pixels is a recommended minimum. Supports PNG, JPEG and GIF formats. Should not be used if og:image:url is used.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--image-src" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Image</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:image_src]</a></td><td>An image associated with this page, for use as a thumbnail in social networks and other services.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--og--image--url" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Image URL</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:og:image:url]</a></td><td>A alternative version of og:image and has exactly the same requirements; only one needs to be used.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--og--image--height" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Image height</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:og:image:height]</a></td><td>The height of the above image(s). Note: if both the unsecured and secured images are provided, they should both be the same size.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--og--image--type" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Image type</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:og:image:type]</a></td><td>The type of image referenced above. Should be either "image/gif" for a GIF image, "image/jpeg" for a JPG/JPEG image, or "image/png" for a PNG image. Note: there should be one value for each image, and having more than there are images may cause problems.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--og--image--width" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Image width</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:og:image:width]</a></td><td>The width of the above image(s). Note: if both the unsecured and secured images are provided, they should both be the same size.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--keywords" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Keywords</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:keywords]</a></td><td>A comma-separated list of keywords about the page. This meta tag is <em>not</em> supported by most search engines anymore.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--profile--last-name" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Last name</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:profile:last_name]</a></td><td>The person's last name.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--og--latitude" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Latitude</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:og:latitude]</a></td><td></td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--og--locale" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Locale</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:og:locale]</a></td><td>The locale these tags are marked up in, must be in the format language_TERRITORY. Default is en_US.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--og--locality" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Locality</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:og:locality]</a></td><td></td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--og--longitude" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Longitude</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:og:longitude]</a></td><td></td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--next" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Next page URL</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:next]</a></td><td>Used for paginated content. Meet Google recommendations to <a href="https://support.google.com/webmasters/answer/1663744">indicate paginated content</a> by providing URL with rel="next" link.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--original-source" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Original Source</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:original-source]</a></td><td>Used to indicate the URL that broke the story, and can link to either an internal URL or an external source. If the full URL is not known it is acceptable to use a partial URL or just the domain name.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--og--url" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Page URL</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:og:url]</a></td><td>Preferred page location or URL to help eliminate duplicate content for search engines, e.g., <em>http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0117500/</em>.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--title" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Page title</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:title]</a></td><td>The text to display in the title bar of a visitor's web browser when they view this page. This meta tag may also be used as the title of the page when a visitor bookmarks or favorites this page.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag--og--phone-number" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-taught--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Phone number</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-taught:metatag:og:phone_number]</a></td><td></td> </tr>

 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag--og--audio--secure-url" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Audio secure URL</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-of-interest:metatag:og:audio:secure_url]</a></td><td>The secure URL to an audio file that complements this object. All "http://" URLs will automatically be converted to "https://".</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag--og--audio--type" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Audio type</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-of-interest:metatag:og:audio:type]</a></td><td>The MIME type of the audio file. Examples include "application/mp3" for an MP3 file.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag--author" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Author URL</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-of-interest:metatag:author]</a></td><td>Used by some search engines to confirm authorship of the content on a page. Should be either the full URL for the author's Google+ profile page or a local page with information about the author.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag--book--isbn" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Book's ISBN</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-of-interest:metatag:book:isbn]</a></td><td>The book's <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number">International Standard Book Number</a>, which may be in one of several formats.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag--book--author" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Book's author</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-of-interest:metatag:book:author]</a></td><td>Links to the book's author's Facebook profile, should be either URLs to the author's profile page or their Facebook profile IDs.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag--book--release-date" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Book release date</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-of-interest:metatag:book:release_date]</a></td><td>The date this content will expire, with an optional time value. Needs to be in <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_8601">ISO 8601</a> format.</td> </tr>

 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag--canonical" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Canonical URL</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-of-interest:metatag:canonical]</a></td><td>Preferred page location or URL to help eliminate duplicate content for search engines.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag--og--description" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Content description</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-of-interest:metatag:og:description]</a></td><td>A one to two sentence description of the content.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag--content-language" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Content language</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-of-interest:metatag:content-language]</a></td><td>A deprecated meta tag for defining this page's two-letter language code(s).</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag--og--updated-time" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Content modification date &amp; time</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-of-interest:metatag:og:updated_time]</a></td><td>The date this content was last modified, with an optional time value. Needs to be in <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_8601">ISO 8601</a> format. Can be the same as the 'Article modification date' tag.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag--rating" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Content rating</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-of-interest:metatag:rating]</a></td><td>Used to indicate the intended audience for the content.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag--og--title" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Content title</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-of-interest:metatag:og:title]</a></td><td>The title of the content, e.g., <em>The Rock</em>.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag--og--determiner" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Content title determiner</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-of-interest:metatag:og:determiner]</a></td><td>The word that appears before the content's title in a sentence. The default ignores this value, the 'Automatic' value should be sufficient if this is actually needed.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag--og--type" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Content type</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-of-interest:metatag:og:type]</a></td><td>The type of the content, e.g., <em>movie</em>.</td> </tr>

The description meta tag may be used by search engines to display a snippet about the page in search results.</td> </tr>

 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag--profile--gender" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Gender</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-of-interest:metatag:profile:gender]</a></td><td>Any of Facebook's gender values should be allowed, the initial two being 'male' and 'female'.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag--generator" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Generator</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-of-interest:metatag:generator]</a></td><td>Describes the name and version number of the software or publishing tool used to create the page.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag--geo.placename" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Geo place name</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-of-interest:metatag:geo.placename]</a></td><td>A location's formal name.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag--geo.position" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Geo position</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-of-interest:metatag:geo.position]</a></td><td>Geo-spatial information in "latitude;longitude" format, e.g. "50.167958;-97.133185"; <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Geotagging#HTML_pages">see Wikipedia for details</a>.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag--geo.region" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Geo region</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-of-interest:metatag:geo.region]</a></td><td>A location's two-letter international country code, with an optional two-letter region, e.g. "US-NH" for New Hampshire in the USA.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag--news-keywords" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Google News Keywords</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-of-interest:metatag:news_keywords]</a></td><td>A comma-separated list of keywords about the page. This meta tag is used as an indicator in <a href="http://support.google.com/news/publisher/bin/answer.py?hl=en&amp;answer=68297">Google News</a>.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag--standout" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Google Standout</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-of-interest:metatag:standout]</a></td><td>Highlight standout journalism on the web, especially for breaking news; used as an indicator in <a href="https://support.google.com/news/publisher/answer/191283?hl=en&amp;ref_topic=2484650">Google News</a>. Warning: Don't abuse it, to be used a maximum of 7 times per calendar week!</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag--icbm" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>ICBM</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-of-interest:metatag:icbm]</a></td><td>Geo-spatial information in "latitude, longitude" format, e.g. "50.167958, -97.133185"; <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ICBM">see Wikipedia for details</a>.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag--og--image" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Image</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-of-interest:metatag:og:image]</a></td><td>The URL of an image which should represent the content. For best results use an image that is at least 1200 x 630 pixels in size, but at least 600 x 316 pixels is a recommended minimum. Supports PNG, JPEG and GIF formats. Should not be used if og:image:url is used.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag--image-src" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Image</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-of-interest:metatag:image_src]</a></td><td>An image associated with this page, for use as a thumbnail in social networks and other services.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag--og--image--url" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Image URL</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-of-interest:metatag:og:image:url]</a></td><td>A alternative version of og:image and has exactly the same requirements; only one needs to be used.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag--og--image--height" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Image height</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-of-interest:metatag:og:image:height]</a></td><td>The height of the above image(s). Note: if both the unsecured and secured images are provided, they should both be the same size.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag--og--image--type" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Image type</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-of-interest:metatag:og:image:type]</a></td><td>The type of image referenced above. Should be either "image/gif" for a GIF image, "image/jpeg" for a JPG/JPEG image, or "image/png" for a PNG image. Note: there should be one value for each image, and having more than there are images may cause problems.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag--og--image--width" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Image width</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-of-interest:metatag:og:image:width]</a></td><td>The width of the above image(s). Note: if both the unsecured and secured images are provided, they should both be the same size.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag--keywords" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Keywords</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-of-interest:metatag:keywords]</a></td><td>A comma-separated list of keywords about the page. This meta tag is <em>not</em> supported by most search engines anymore.</td> </tr>

 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag--og--locale" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Locale</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-of-interest:metatag:og:locale]</a></td><td>The locale these tags are marked up in, must be in the format language_TERRITORY.  <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag--next" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Next page URL</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-of-interest:metatag:next]</a></td><td>Used for paginated content.  <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag--original-source" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Original Source</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-of-interest:metatag:original-source]</a></td><td>Used to indicate the URL that broke the story, and can link to either an internal URL or an external source. If the full URL is not known it is acceptable to use a partial URL or just the domain name.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag--og--url" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-language-of-interest--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Page URL</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-language-of-interest:metatag:og:url]</a></td><td>Preferred page location or URL to help eliminate duplicate content for search engines, e.g., <em>http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0117500/</em>.</td> </tr>

This meta tag may also be used as the title of the page when a visitor bookmarks or favorites this page.</td> </tr>

Warning: Don't abuse it, to be used a maximum of 7 times per calendar week!</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-userlanguage--metatag--icbm" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-userlanguage--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>ICBM</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-userlanguage:metatag:icbm]</a></td><td>Geo-spatial information in "latitude, longitude" format, e.g. "50.167958, -97.133185"; <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ICBM">see Wikipedia for details</a>.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-userlanguage--metatag--og--image" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-userlanguage--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Image</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-userlanguage:metatag:og:image]</a></td><td>The URL of an image which should represent the content. For best results use an image that is at least 1200 x 630 pixels in size, but at least 600 x 316 pixels is a recommended minimum. Supports PNG, JPEG and GIF formats. Should not be used if og:image:url is used.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-userlanguage--metatag--image-src" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-userlanguage--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Image</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-userlanguage:metatag:image_src]</a></td><td>An image associated with this page, for use as a thumbnail in social networks and other services.</td> </tr>

 <tr id="token-current-user--field-userlanguage--metatag--og--image--height" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-userlanguage--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Image height</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-userlanguage:metatag:og:image:height]</a></td><td>The height of the above image(s).  <tr id="token-current-user--field-userlanguage--metatag--og--image--type" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-userlanguage--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Image type</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-userlanguage:metatag:og:image:type]</a></td><td>The type of image referenced above. Should be either "image/gif" for a GIF image, "image/jpeg" for a JPG/JPEG image, or "image/png" for a PNG image. Note: there should be one value for each image, and having more than there are images may cause problems.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-current-user--field-userlanguage--metatag--og--image--width" class="child-of-token-current-user--field-userlanguage--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Image width</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[current-user:field-userlanguage:metatag:og:image:width]</a></td><td>The width of the above image(s). Warning: Don't abuse it, to be used a maximum of 7 times per calendar week!</td> </tr>

 <tr id="token-metatag--og--image" class="child-of-token-metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td style="padding-left: 28px;">Image</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[metatag:og:image]</a></td><td>The URL of an image which should represent the content. For best results use an image that is at least 1200 x 630 pixels in size, but at least 600 x 316 pixels is a recommended minimum. Supports PNG, JPEG and GIF formats. Should not be used if og:image:url is used.</td> </tr>

 <tr id="token-metatag--og--image--height" class="child-of-token-metatag even" style="display: none;"><td style="padding-left: 28px;">Image height</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[metatag:og:image:height]</a></td><td>The height of the above image(s).  <tr id="token-metatag--og--image--type" class="child-of-token-metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td style="padding-left: 28px;">Image type</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[metatag:og:image:type]</a></td><td>The type of image referenced above. Should be either "image/gif" for a GIF image, "image/jpeg" for a JPG/JPEG image, or "image/png" for a PNG image. Note: there should be one value for each image, and having more than there are images may cause problems.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-metatag--og--image--width" class="child-of-token-metatag even" style="display: none;"><td style="padding-left: 28px;">Image width</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[metatag:og:image:width]</a></td><td>The width of the above image(s).  <tr id="token-privatemsg-message--feed-node--metatag--og--audio--secure-url" class="child-of-token-privatemsg-message--feed-node--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Audio secure URL</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[privatemsg_message:feed-node:metatag:og:audio:secure_url]</a></td><td>The secure URL to an audio file that complements this object. All "http://" URLs will automatically be converted to "https://".</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-privatemsg-message--feed-node--metatag--og--audio--type" class="child-of-token-privatemsg-message--feed-node--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Audio type</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[privatemsg_message:feed-node:metatag:og:audio:type]</a></td><td>The MIME type of the audio file. Examples include "application/mp3" for an MP3 file.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-privatemsg-message--feed-node--metatag--author" class="child-of-token-privatemsg-message--feed-node--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Author URL</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[privatemsg_message:feed-node:metatag:author]</a></td><td>Used by some search engines to confirm authorship of the content on a page. Should be either the full URL for the author's Google+ profile page or a local page with information about the author.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-privatemsg-message--feed-node--metatag--book--isbn" class="child-of-token-privatemsg-message--feed-node--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Book's ISBN</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[privatemsg_message:feed-node:metatag:book:isbn]</a></td><td>The book's <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number">International Standard Book Number</a>, which may be in one of several formats.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-privatemsg-message--feed-node--metatag--book--author" class="child-of-token-privatemsg-message--feed-node--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Book's author</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[privatemsg_message:feed-node:metatag:book:author]</a></td><td>Links to the book's author's Facebook profile, should be either URLs to the author's profile page or their Facebook profile IDs.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-privatemsg-message--feed-node--metatag--book--release-date" class="child-of-token-privatemsg-message--feed-node--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Book release date</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[privatemsg_message:feed-node:metatag:book:release_date]</a></td><td>The date this content will expire, with an optional time value. Needs to be in <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_8601">ISO 8601</a> format.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-privatemsg-message--feed-node--metatag--book--tag" class="child-of-token-privatemsg-message--feed-node--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Book tags</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[privatemsg_message:feed-node:metatag:book:tag]</a></td><td>Appropriate keywords for this book.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-privatemsg-message--feed-node--metatag--canonical" class="child-of-token-privatemsg-message--feed-node--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Canonical URL</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[privatemsg_message:feed-node:metatag:canonical]</a></td><td>Preferred page location or URL to help eliminate duplicate content for search engines.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-privatemsg-message--feed-node--metatag--og--description" class="child-of-token-privatemsg-message--feed-node--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Content description</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[privatemsg_message:feed-node:metatag:og:description]</a></td><td>A one to two sentence description of the content.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-privatemsg-message--feed-node--metatag--content-language" class="child-of-token-privatemsg-message--feed-node--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Content language</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[privatemsg_message:feed-node:metatag:content-language]</a></td><td>A deprecated meta tag for defining this page's two-letter language code(s).</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-privatemsg-message--feed-node--metatag--og--updated-time" class="child-of-token-privatemsg-message--feed-node--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Content modification date &amp; time</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[privatemsg_message:feed-node:metatag:og:updated_time]</a></td><td>The date this content was last modified, with an optional time value. Needs to be in <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_8601">ISO 8601</a> format. Can be the same as the 'Article modification date' tag.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-privatemsg-message--feed-node--metatag--rating" class="child-of-token-privatemsg-message--feed-node--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Content rating</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[privatemsg_message:feed-node:metatag:rating]</a></td><td>Used to indicate the intended audience for the content.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-privatemsg-message--feed-node--metatag--og--title" class="child-of-token-privatemsg-message--feed-node--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Content title</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[privatemsg_message:feed-node:metatag:og:title]</a></td><td>The title of the content, e.g., <em>The Rock</em>.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-privatemsg-message--feed-node--metatag--og--determiner" class="child-of-token-privatemsg-message--feed-node--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Content title determiner</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[privatemsg_message:feed-node:metatag:og:determiner]</a></td><td>The word that appears before the content's title in a sentence. The default ignores this value, the 'Automatic' value should be sufficient if this is actually needed.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-privatemsg-message--feed-node--metatag--og--type" class="child-of-token-privatemsg-message--feed-node--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Content type</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[privatemsg_message:feed-node:metatag:og:type]</a></td><td>The type of the content, e.g., <em>movie</em>.</td> </tr>

 <tr id="token-privatemsg-message--feed-node--metatag--description" class="child-of-token-privatemsg-message--feed-node--metatag odd" style="display: none;"><td>Description</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[privatemsg_message:feed-node:metatag:description]</a></td><td>A brief and concise summary of the page's content, preferably 150 characters or less. The description meta tag may be used by search engines to display a snippet about the page in search results.</td> </tr>
 <tr id="token-privatemsg-message--feed-node--metatag--video--director" class="child-of-token-privatemsg-message--feed-node--metatag even" style="display: none;"><td>Director(s)</td><td class="token-key token-click-insert-processed"><a href="javascript:void(0);" title="Insert this token into your form">[privatemsg_message:feed-node:metatag:video:director]</a></td><td>Links to the Facebook profiles for director(s) that worked on the video.</td> </tr>
